The paper discusses the use of an automatic summarization system coupled with a question answering system, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
